All Implemented Interfaces:
DataOutput, ObjectOutput, ObjectStreamConstants
public class CacheOutputStream
extends ObjectOutputStream

An ObjectOutputStream which supports sharing objects with other CacheOutputStream(s). When multiple ObjectIntputStreams serialize the same object, a complete (deep) representation of the object is placed in the separate streams. This implementation avoids that problem, but does assume that access by multiple threads is protected above (in the object hierarchy)
